# TxTWrapðŸ”¡
A tool for wrapping a text.ðŸ”¨

> **âš ï¸All documents are in the each module.âš ï¸**

All constants and functionsâ•:
- `LOREM_IPSUM_W`
- `LOREM_IPSUM_S`
- `LOREM_IPSUM_P`
- `mono`
- `word`
- `wrap`
- `align` (Updated!)
- `fillstr`
